snippet.title: Johnny Depp performs with Hollywood Vampires in Portugal hours after Amber Heard accuses him
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp performs with Hollywood Vampires in Portugal hours after Amber Heard accuses him 

 Johnny Depp appeared to be in good spirits when he joined his band the Hollywood Vampires on stage on Friday night.

Hours earlier his estranged wife Amber Heard had accused him of domestic violence during a dramatic court hearing which took place five days after she filed for divorce.

Shrugging off the allegations, the actor took to the stage as the legendary group headlined the Rock in Rio Festival at Bela Vista Park in Lisbon, Portugal.

The seven-strong group wowed the crowds before Johnny posed for pictures with his famous bandmates, including Alice Cooper and Joe Perry.

snippet.title: "When I Live My Life Over Again" Q&A at the 2015 Gold Coast International Film Festival
snippet.description:
Q&A with director Robert Edwards

After one too many big city problems, Jude (Amber Heard) heads to the Hamptons home of her father (Christopher Walken), an over-the-hill crooner desperately charting his musical comeback. She soon recalls that spending time at home with her father presents its own particular set of challenges. Writer-director Robert Edwards (Land of the Blind) perfectly captures the inner turmoil of an aspiring artist through his characterization of Jude and Robert, demonstrating that ambition isn’t enough to get what you want. Amber Heard commands the screen as a charming singer-songwriter who temporarily retires her rose-colored glasses for rose-colored hair. —Ashley Havey, Tribeca Film Festival

snippet.title: Love Island's Amber Gill, Anna Vakili and Yewande Biala are 'not sure' if they will watch new winter
snippet.description: They rose to fame on the summer series of Love Island. But winner Amber Gill and her BFF's Anna Vakili and Yewande Biala admitted they're not sure if they will watch the brand new winter series of the hit ITV2 show. It comes after Caroline Flack, 40, stepped down as host after being charged with assaulting her toyboy boyfriend Lewis Burton, 27, at her London home earlier this month.     When asked by Ben Shepherd: 'Will you watch winter series?', the host was met with deadly silence.  Amber was the first to answer: 'I will be, yeah, I am going to try,' while Anna, 29, rather unconvincingly said: 'I am going to try, see it from a different perspective. Now you’ve been in it, it’s different, you see it all.' During their appearance, the girls also spoke about the advice they would give to any islanders.    Amber said: 'What I would do differently if I could turn back time, don’t take everything to heart or too seriously. 'Take it more lighthearted and fun. I kept it real, I am not sure if that is a good or bad thing.'Yewande added: 'Just enjoy it, everyone said to me, enjoy it, I didn’t understand. When you come out, you realise I’ve had the most amazing experience not everyone gets to have. Enjoy each day, be happy and just enjoy.'   Amber, who shortly split from Greg O'Shea after winning the show, concluded: 'Just keep it real, always be yourself. Stay true to yourself, don’t be hung up on winning, just stick to what feels right.' The trio's appearance comes after Caroline pleaded not guilty to assaulting her boyfriend, 27, at Highbury Magistrates' Court on Monday. Caroline and her partner were both allegedly covered in blood when police arrived at their flat in Islington, North London, on December 12 - with one officer describing the chaotic scene as 'like a horror movie'.   On Monday she pleaded not guilty to common assault and was released on bail until her trial in March but is not allowed to contact Lewis. The presenter was accused of 'going mad' and smashing a glass after looking at texts which made her think Lewis was cheating - with him saying in a 999 call that she 'tried to kill me, mate', Highbury Corner Magistrates' Court heard.Lewis was said to have been 'almost begging the operator to send help' with his face 'covered in blood', while Caroline - who has now been replaced as Love Island host by Laura Whitmore - allegedly had two cuts to her wrist.  After being taken into custody, ITV host Caroline - whom the court heard was 'manipulative' towards Lewis and accused him of ruining her life - allegedly flipped over a table and had to be restrained on the ground by police.  In the wake of the drama, Caroline stepped down from her hosting duties and Laura Whitmore was announced as her replacement.

snippet.title: Love Island's Amber Gill laments life as a singleton as reality star reveals she has nobody at home
snippet.description: Amber Gill playfully lamented her life as a singleton on Wednesday, when she complained about not having anybody to chat with on FaceTime.The Love Island winner, 22, is currently soaking up the sunshine on the Caribbean island of Tobago with her sister Lauren, but took to her Instagram Stories to suggest she'd have been happier if she had a man at home waiting for her.As bikini-clad Amber enjoyed a quiet boat ride, she shared footage of her sister enjoying a video call, before panning back to her own face in a clip captioned: 'When everyone's FaceTiming and you have nobody to FaceTime.'   Wearing a flattering turquoise bikini, the Geordie beauty – whose father's side of her family hails from Trinidad and Tobago – pulled a series of comedic facial expressions as she stood in complete silence. Amber rose to prominence when she was crowned the winner of Love Island last year alongside Greg O' Shea, but the couple split just weeks after leaving the villa. Last week, it was claimed that she was dating Chelsea and England footballer  Fikayo Tomori, after she was seen leaving flirty comments on his Instagram.  The former beauty therapist is said to have been on a string of dates with Fikayo in London and he has already reportedly met some of her close friends.The pair set tongues wagging last Thursday, after Amber left a suggestive comment on one of his social media snaps after her 'liked' one of her bikini photos.A friend of Amber's told the Sun: 'They've been on two dates in as many weeks in London... They've been chatting for quite a while now but only recently met properly. 'The fact she has posted a public display of affection, by flirting on Instagram, is a good sign too. She's not usually one to show her feelings so quickly.'  This comes after cheeky Amber commented 'drip drip,' to which the footballer replied 'don't drown' under a photo Fikayo shared of himself sitting in a flash car.'Surely you guys should couple up,' commented one excited fan. However, Amber has since insisted that the pair are just friends.Amber has been unlucky in love since winning the 2019 series of Love Island with her then beau Greg O'Shea, only for the couple to split weeks after they left the villa. Greg entered the villa as a late arrival and immediately caught Amber's eye, as she ultimately decided to couple up with him rather than Michael Griffiths.  However it was a short lived romance for the pair, as Greg ditched Amber via text citing the distance between them as the reason behind their split.Elsewhere, Michael recently sparked dating rumours with her close friend Ellie Brown.During an appearance on Under the Duvet with VOXI, Amber chatted with her pal Anna Vakili about romances after the show, but remained tight-lipped about Michael and Ellie.During the chat - which also included Amy Hart - Anna asked if Michael, 28, was 'with' Ellie, 21, saying that she was confused.  Amy then said she thought they had split and Anna added: 'Well I heard otherwise. Ellie used t

snippet.title: 3 DAYS TO KILL/ Su Rai 2 il film con Amber Heard e Kevin Costner (oggi, 30 aprile 2018)
snippet.description:
3 DAYS TO KILL/ Su Rai 2 il film con Amber Heard e Kevin Costner (oggi, 30 aprile 2018)
❖ Help Us to Get 50.000 Subscribers
🔔 Hope you like it. Click Like and Subscribe My Channel. Thanks :D
▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬
3 Days To Kill, il film in onda su Rai 2 oggi, lunedì 30 aprile 2018 alle ore 21.20. Una pellicola di genere thriller del 2014 che è stata diretta da McG, nome d'arte di Joseph McGinty Nichol (Terminator salvation, Charlie's Angels, Una spia non basta) ed interpretata da Amber Heard (Justice League, Never back down - Mai arrendersi, London fields), Kevin Costner (Guardia del corpo, Balla coi lupi, Robin Hood - Principe dei ladri) e Hailee Steinfeld (The dege of seventeen, Pitch perfect 2 e 3, Il Grinta). Soggetto e sceneggiatura sono stati scritti da Luc Besson (Valerian e la città dei mille pianeti, Leon, Il quinto elemento), presente anche nelle vesti di produttore. Secondo le critiche il film soffre di una mancanza di direzione. Da una parte si tratta di un action movie senile, con tutti i luoghi comuni dell'eroe al tramonto e l'ultima missione che dovrebbe salvargli la vita e garantirgli una vecchiaia di pace e serenità. D'altra parte il film cerca di contaminare questa base action con la commedia e il melodramma della gestione famigliare e del rapporto fra Ethan e la figlia Zoey, cresciuta praticamente senza un padre e che ora lo vede scomparire, dopo avergli promesso un ultimo periodo insieme, per l'ennesima missione segreta e pericolosa. Ma ecco nel dettaglio la trama del film.

snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Tie the Knot: Source
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard made it legal at their home in Los Angeles on Tuesday, a source tells PEOPLE. 

As previously reported, a bigger wedding is still to come this weekend on Depp's private island (Little Hall's Pond Cay) in the Bahamas. 

Depp, 51, and Heard, 28, got engaged over the holidays in 2012 after meeting on the set of 2011's The Rum Diary. 

They stepped out as a couple in 2012 after the actor split with longtime partner Vanessa Paradis, and though they weathered split rumors late last year, the two have seemed better than ever as of late, showing off PDA at various events.

snippet.title: AMBER HEARD - హాలీవుడ్ లోనూ భార్య‌ల‌కు భ‌ర్త‌ల చేతిలో చావు దెబ్బ‌లు..
snippet.description:
హాలీవుడ్ లోనూ భార్య‌ల‌కు భ‌ర్త‌ల చేతిలో చావు దెబ్బ‌లు..


ఎంత స్టార్ హీరో అయినా కొడితే ఎవరు పడి ఉంటారు. అందులోనూ తాగి వచ్చి రోజూ చితకొడుతూంటే ఎదురు తిరగాలి అనిపిస్తుంది. అయితే ఆ కసిని మనస్సులో పెట్టుకుని పెద్ద మొత్తంలో భరణం సొమ్ములాగి, దాన్ని తన లాగ భాధపడేవారికి, ఛారిటీలకు ఇచ్చి కసి తీర్చుకుందామె. ఈ స్టోరీ ఎవరి గురించి, ఎవరా స్టార్ హీరో అంటారా..ఇంకెవరు మనకందరికీ తెలుసున్న హాలీవుడ్ స్టార్ హీరో జానీ డెప్ గురించి. అవును.. పైరేట్స్ ఆఫ్ ద కరేబియన్ సిరీస్ లో కెప్టెన్ జాక్ స్పారో పాత్రలో విభిన్న శైలిలో నటించి మెప్పించిన డెప్ గురించే ఇదంతా. కిందటేడాది ఫిబ్రవరిలో, మూడేళ్ల రొమాంటిక్‌ డేట్స్‌ తర్వాత జానీడెప్ వివాహమాడిన యాంబర్‌ హెర్డ్‌, ఇప్పుడు విడాకులు కావాలంటూ కోర్టుకెక్కింది. తనను డెప్‌ ఇంట్లో చావగొడుతున్నాడనీ, ఈ మధ్యనే తన సెల్‌ఫోన్‌ను విసిరి, నుదుటి మీద గాయం చేశాడనీ ఆమె అభియోగం. చివరకు విడాకలు అయ్యాయి. అయితే కోర్టులో విషయం నడుస్తున్నప్పుడు.. యాంబర్ మీదనే నిందలు వేశాడు జానీ డెప్. వాటిన్నటినీ తట్టుకోలేకపోయిందో మరేమో కానీ .. ఇప్పుడు జానీ డెప్ ఈ అమ్మడును కొడుతున్న రెండు మూడు వీడియోలు బయటకు వచ్చేశాయి. వాటినే సాక్ష్యాలుగా పరిగణిస్తూ కోర్టు దాదాపు డైవర్స్ ఖరారుచేసినట్లే. ఇకపోతే భరణం క్రింద యాంబర్ హర్డ్ ఏకంగా 7 మిలియన్ డాలర్లు (దాదాపు 45 కోట్లు) తీసుకుంటోంది. అయితే ఇక్కడ ట్విస్ట్ ఏమిటి అంటే.. ఈ 7 మిలియన్లు చేతికి అందగానే వాటిని యథాతథంగ ఒక చారిటీ సంస్థకు ఇచ్చేస్తోంది. చారిటీకి ఇచ్చేయడానికి కావల్సిన పత్రాలను కూడా సైన్ చేసింది యాంబర్.

snippet.title: Amber Heard « aime frapper » : ce jour où Johnny Depp a fini en larmes chez son voisin
snippet.description: À chaque jour son lot de rebondissements. Johnny Depp, qui accuse le journal The Sun de diffamation suite à la parution en 2018 d'un article où il était qualifié de "batteur de femmes", doit prouver que contrairement à ce que son ex-femme Amber Heard clame, il n'a jamais levé la main sur elle. Depuis quelques jours maintenant, les témoins se succèdent à la Cour royale de justice de Londres et livrent une toute autre version des faits. Ce vendredi 17 juillet, c'était au tour d'Isaac Baruch, voisin et ami de l'acteur, de témoigner. L'artiste s'est notamment souvenu d'une nuit où l'ex de Vanessa Paradis, en larmes, lui a fait part de sa détresse, comme le révèle le Mirror. Intime de l'acteur de Pirates des Caraïbes depuis quarante ans, Isaac Baruch a déclaré que ce dernier avait frappé à sa porte un soir de 2013 avec "l'air déprimé et un peu désemparé, comme s'il pleurait". À ce moment, Johnny Depp lui aurait alors confié qu'Amber Heard aimait "se disputer et frapper". Incrédule, son am ...

snippet.title: Amber Heard chiama la polizia “Johnny Depp sta portando via degli oggetti da casa nostra”
snippet.description:
Amber Heard chiama la polizia: “Johnny Depp sta portando via degli oggetti da casa nostra”
Secondo quanto riportato da TMZ, Amber Heard avrebbe chiamato la polizia perché delle persone vicine a Johnny Depp si sarebbero introdotte nella loro casa di Los Angeles per portare via mobili e oggetti appartenenti all'attore. Inoltre, nei documenti legali, ha tuonato contro l'ex compagno: "Parla degli alimenti per distrarre l'attenzione dei media dalla violenza domestica".

snippet.title: Amber Heard posts topless Insta pic from Bali vacation
snippet.description: American actress Amber Heard has landed in Bali and there are pics to prove iteven a topless one.  Dont get too excited though, the 31-year-old ex-wife of Johnny Depp kept it tasteful and just posed in her bikini bottoms at what appears to be a private rooftop pool, with her back to the camera, simply captioning the shot, When in Bali. A post shared by Amber Heard (@amberheard) on Sep 11, 2017 at 7:22am PDTApparently recovering from her recent breakup from billionaire boyfriend Elon Musk, Heard is accompanied in Bali by close friend Raquel Pennington and assistant, Savannah McMillan. Theres a video of Heard and Pennington donning matching white outfits, getting their groove on to some Balinese beats, with the two swinging their hips to the music.  Indonesian Instagrammers seem thrilled to see Heard in the archipelago nation, with a number of comments on her video reading Welcome to Bali!. Hello Bali!A post shared by Amber Heard (@amberheard) on Sep 10, 2017 at 8:03am PDTIn the same outfits, the two pose in a black and white shot, and another photo posted to Heards account shows them eating sashimi.
